}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:90:\"https://theeventscalendar.com/blog/news/how-to-embed-facebook-live-on-your-wordpress-site/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 26 Oct 2021 17:57:05 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"What\'s New\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"https://theeventscalendar.com/?p=2321157\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:627:\"<p>Generating fresh video content for your users is essential to keeping them engaged with your brand. Lots of popular options like YouTube Live and Instagram Stories allow you to connect with followers in real-time. Even better, you can add Facebook Live directly to your WordPress site so that users can find out about your event&#8230;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/blog/news/how-to-embed-facebook-live-on-your-wordpress-site/\">How to Embed Facebook Live on Your WordPress Site</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com\">The Events Calendar</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Jaime\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9274:\"\n<p>Generating fresh video content for your users is essential to keeping them engaged with your brand. Lots of popular options like <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/knowledgebase/k/connecting-to-youtube-live/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">YouTube Live</a> and <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/blog/event-management/how-event-planners-can-use-facebook-and-instagrams-new-live-event-features/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Instagram Stories</a> allow you to connect with followers in real-time. Even better, you can <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/knowledgebase/k/connecting-to-facebook-live/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">add Facebook Live</a> directly to your WordPress site so that users can find out about your event and watch it all in one place.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Our <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/products/wordpress-virtual-events/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Virtual Events</a> plugin now comes with a <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/release-notes/virtual-events/virtual-events-1-7-0/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Facebook Live integration</a> ready to help you embed your livestream directly on your event page. Once you’re synced with Facebook, you can easily take your live events from your Facebook Page to your WordPress event page. Select your Facebook Page from the dropdown options for video sources any time you’d like to include Facebook Live on your event page.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Below, we’ll talk about the benefits of using <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/formedia/solutions/facebook-live\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Facebook Live</a> on your WordPress site and how to use Virtual Events for all of your online event needs.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-the-benefits-of-facebook-live\">The benefits of Facebook Live</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Facebook Live is a <a href=\"https://www.responsiveinboundmarketing.com/blog/10-pros-and-cons-of-facebook-live\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">fantastic tool</a> for hosting live events. It allows you to interact with attendees throughout your broadcast to get their reactions, comments, and questions. It’s also a great way to gain new subscribers, engage in unexpected and important conversations, and earn valuable exposure in your area of expertise. All while saving money since Facebook Live has no overhead costs.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-facebook-live-and-wordpress-working-together\">Facebook Live and WordPress working together</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If people aren’t already subscribed to your Facebook Page, they don’t know where to find your events. Using your website as a marketing tool is the most effective method for helping potential consumers understand what it is that you do. What&#8217;s great is that your branding will already be incorporated on your WordPress site, so users can get a sense of what you&#8217;re all about and feel like they&#8217;re buying into your brand when they decide to tune in to your Facebook Live event.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>By setting up your event page with your embedded livestream, users know exactly when to tune in to your event so that they don’t miss a beat.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pro tip:</strong> Take things to the next level with <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/products/wordpress-event-tickets/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Event Tickets Plus</a>. Sell tickets to your events and monetize your livestreams entirely from your WordPress site.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-leverage-facebook-live-to-your-advantage\">Leverage Facebook Live to your advantage</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We’ve seen some <a href=\"https://www.impactplus.com/blog/facebook-live-business-examples\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">superb examples</a> of how to use Facebook Live to promote campaigns, host AMAs (Ask Me Anything), and share workout classes. For small businesses, we know that obtaining exposure is critical, so why not capitalize on your WordPress site’s traffic in order to gain followers? Easily utilize the built-in schema optimization available with our Virtual Events plugin to make your live events discoverable on Google.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"1032\" height=\"1210\" src=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.15-PM.png\" alt=\"Spirit and Place uses Facebook Live on their WordPress site.\" class=\"wp-image-2321161\" srcset=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.15-PM.png 1032w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.15-PM-256x300.png 256w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.15-PM-665x780.png 665w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.15-PM-72x85.png 72w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.15-PM-768x900.png 768w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.15-PM-430x504.png 430w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.15-PM-645x756.png 645w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.15-PM-460x539.png 460w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.15-PM-512x600.png 512w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.15-PM-940x1102.png 940w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.15-PM-452x530.png 452w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.15-PM-300x352.png 300w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.15-PM-600x703.png 600w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.15-PM-500x586.png 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1032px) 100vw, 1032px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"1044\" height=\"1084\" src=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.35-PM.png\" alt=\"Spirit and Place uses Facebook Live to host virtual events on their WordPress site.\" class=\"wp-image-2321162\" srcset=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.35-PM.png 1044w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.35-PM-289x300.png 289w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.35-PM-665x690.png 665w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.35-PM-82x85.png 82w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.35-PM-768x797.png 768w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.35-PM-430x446.png 430w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.35-PM-645x670.png 645w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.35-PM-460x478.png 460w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.35-PM-512x532.png 512w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.35-PM-510x530.png 510w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.35-PM-300x311.png 300w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.35-PM-600x623.png 600w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-20-at-12.43.35-PM-500x519.png 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1044px) 100vw, 1044px\" /><figcaption><a href=\"https://spiritandplace.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Spirit and Place</a> broadcasts their events on Facebook Live with Virtual Events.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-virtual-events-to-the-rescue\">Virtual Events to the rescue <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.1.0/72x72/1f680.png\" alt=\"🚀\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Starting a Facebook livestream is as easy as clicking a single button. With just a few extra clicks, <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/products/wordpress-virtual-events/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Virtual Events</a> allows you to integrate Facebook Live right onto your WordPress site.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And there’s even more to love with our Virtual Events plugin! With it, you can effortlessly embed a YouTube Live link, <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/knowledgebase/k/security-and-protected-content-for-virtual-events/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">create protected content</a> for only your attendees to view, and even integrate your <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/knowledgebase/k/connecting-to-zoom/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Zoom meetings</a> onto your WordPress site.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/blog/news/how-to-embed-facebook-live-on-your-wordpress-site/\">How to Embed Facebook Live on Your WordPress Site</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com\">The Events Calendar</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"How to Use Shortcodes to Create Multiple Calendars on Your WordPress Site\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:114:\"https://theeventscalendar.com/blog/tips/how-to-use-shortcodes-to-create-multiple-calendars-on-your-wordpress-site/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 21 Oct 2021 14:59:47 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Tips & Tricks\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"https://theeventscalendar.com/?p=2320777\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:671:\"<p>Shortcodes are small pieces of code that pack a punch. They allow you to add functionality to your website with a shorthand that your WordPress site can read and interpret without having to write a single line of code. And Events Calendar Pro comes standard with shortcodes. You can use the [tribe_events] shortcode to embed&#8230;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/blog/tips/how-to-use-shortcodes-to-create-multiple-calendars-on-your-wordpress-site/\">How to Use Shortcodes to Create Multiple Calendars on Your WordPress Site</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com\">The Events Calendar</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Jaime\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18155:\"\n<p>Shortcodes are small pieces of code that pack a punch. They allow you to add functionality to your website with a shorthand that your WordPress site can read and interpret without having to write a single line of code.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/products/wordpress-events-calendar/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Events Calendar Pro</a> comes standard with <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/blog/tips/event-calendar-shortcodes-where-to-find/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">shortcodes</a>. You can use the <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/knowledgebase/k/embedding-calendar-views-with-the-tribe_events-shortcode/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">[tribe_events]</a> shortcode to embed a calendar on any WordPress page or post on your website. From there, you can customize each shortcode to only include certain events, venues, organizers, and beyond.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Take it to the next level by adding <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/knowledgebase/k/event-categories/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">event categories</a> to each of your shortcodes. This will allow you to create numerous calendars on a single WordPress install by simply adding a few words to each page.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-the-case-for-categories\">The case for categories</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With event categories, you can arrange and sort your events how you like. Then, you can exhibit individualized calendars throughout your WordPress site based on the categories you created.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For example, if you host workshops, you can utilize categories to display different sorts of workshops on separate pages.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"1866\" height=\"1108\" src=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-7.44.55-AM.png\" alt=\"How to use a shortcode to display category calendars\" class=\"wp-image-2320778\" srcset=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-7.44.55-AM.png 1866w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-7.44.55-AM-300x178.png 300w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-7.44.55-AM-665x395.png 665w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-7.44.55-AM-140x83.png 140w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-7.44.55-AM-768x456.png 768w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-7.44.55-AM-1536x912.png 1536w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-7.44.55-AM-688x410.png 688w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-7.44.55-AM-344x205.png 344w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-7.44.55-AM-430x255.png 430w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-7.44.55-AM-645x383.png 645w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-7.44.55-AM-1068x634.png 1068w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-7.44.55-AM-460x273.png 460w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-7.44.55-AM-1602x951.png 1602w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-7.44.55-AM-1074x638.png 1074w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-7.44.55-AM-512x304.png 512w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-7.44.55-AM-1611x957.png 1611w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-7.44.55-AM-1856x1102.png 1856w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-7.44.55-AM-707x420.png 707w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-7.44.55-AM-600x356.png 600w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-7.44.55-AM-500x297.png 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1866px) 100vw, 1866px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Online mediums Philip Dykes and Kerry McLeod use the <a href=\"https://www.thespiritandsoulfoundation.co.uk/mediumship-workshops/category/weekly-workshops/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Weekly Workshops</a> category shortcode [tribe_events category=“weekly-workshops”] in Photo View to present their recurring workshops.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://duxburystudentunion.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Duxbury Student Union</a> also uses shortcodes with categories to show off its various offerings. Below you’ll see only the half-day camp events. On another page entirely, they feature the full-day camps using a different category shortcode.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"1256\" height=\"1266\" src=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-8.00.21-AM.png\" alt=\"Duxbury Student Union uses category shortcodes to display calendars on their WordPress site\" class=\"wp-image-2320781\" srcset=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-8.00.21-AM.png 1256w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-8.00.21-AM-298x300.png 298w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-8.00.21-AM-665x670.png 665w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-8.00.21-AM-84x85.png 84w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-8.00.21-AM-768x774.png 768w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-8.00.21-AM-430x433.png 430w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-8.00.21-AM-645x650.png 645w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-8.00.21-AM-180x180.png 180w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-8.00.21-AM-1068x1077.png 1068w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-8.00.21-AM-460x464.png 460w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-8.00.21-AM-1074x1083.png 1074w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-8.00.21-AM-512x516.png 512w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-8.00.21-AM-1093x1102.png 1093w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-8.00.21-AM-526x530.png 526w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-8.00.21-AM-150x150.png 150w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-8.00.21-AM-300x302.png 300w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-8.00.21-AM-100x100.png 100w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-8.00.21-AM-600x605.png 600w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-8.00.21-AM-500x504.png 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1256px) 100vw, 1256px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-how-to-add-categories-to-your-events\">How to add categories to your events</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you&#8217;ve seen some stellar examples of how adding category shortcodes to your WordPress site may be beneficial, let&#8217;s go through how to implement this feature on your own site.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/knowledgebase/k/creating-an-event/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">create events</a> as per usual, but this time be sure to choose a pre-existing category or create a new one in the right sidebar with the Block Editor.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"2372\" height=\"1168\" src=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.08.16-AM.png\" alt=\"How to add categories to your events\" class=\"wp-image-2320782\" srcset=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.08.16-AM.png 2372w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.08.16-AM-300x148.png 300w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.08.16-AM-665x327.png 665w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.08.16-AM-140x69.png 140w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.08.16-AM-768x378.png 768w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.08.16-AM-1536x756.png 1536w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.08.16-AM-2048x1008.png 2048w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.08.16-AM-430x212.png 430w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.08.16-AM-645x318.png 645w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.08.16-AM-2000x985.png 2000w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.08.16-AM-1068x526.png 1068w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.08.16-AM-460x227.png 460w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.08.16-AM-1602x789.png 1602w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.08.16-AM-1074x529.png 1074w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.08.16-AM-512x252.png 512w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.08.16-AM-1611x793.png 1611w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.08.16-AM-707x348.png 707w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.08.16-AM-600x295.png 600w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.08.16-AM-500x246.png 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2372px) 100vw, 2372px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, go to Event Categories to find the slug of your category, which you’ll use to build a page of events with just that one category.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"2420\" height=\"840\" src=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.10.48-AM.png\" alt=\"Finding event categories slug on a WordPress site\" class=\"wp-image-2320785\" srcset=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.10.48-AM.png 2420w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.10.48-AM-300x104.png 300w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.10.48-AM-665x231.png 665w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.10.48-AM-140x49.png 140w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.10.48-AM-768x267.png 768w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.10.48-AM-1536x533.png 1536w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.10.48-AM-2048x711.png 2048w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.10.48-AM-430x149.png 430w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.10.48-AM-645x224.png 645w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.10.48-AM-2000x694.png 2000w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.10.48-AM-1068x371.png 1068w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.10.48-AM-460x160.png 460w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.10.48-AM-1602x556.png 1602w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.10.48-AM-1074x373.png 1074w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.10.48-AM-512x178.png 512w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.10.48-AM-1611x559.png 1611w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.10.48-AM-707x245.png 707w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.10.48-AM-600x208.png 600w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.10.48-AM-500x174.png 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2420px) 100vw, 2420px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In this example, we’ll use the Cooking Class category, so the slug that you want is “cooking-class”.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can then use the shortcode [tribe_events category= “cooking-class”] to display all of your events within that category.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Add a new WordPress page or post and include a shortcode block with your desired category shortcode.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"1432\" height=\"642\" src=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.13.53-AM.png\" alt=\"Adding a [tribe_events] category shortcode to your WordPress site\" class=\"wp-image-2320786\" srcset=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.13.53-AM.png 1432w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.13.53-AM-300x134.png 300w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.13.53-AM-665x298.png 665w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.13.53-AM-140x63.png 140w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.13.53-AM-768x344.png 768w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.13.53-AM-430x193.png 430w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.13.53-AM-645x289.png 645w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.13.53-AM-1068x479.png 1068w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.13.53-AM-460x206.png 460w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.13.53-AM-1074x482.png 1074w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.13.53-AM-512x230.png 512w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.13.53-AM-707x317.png 707w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.13.53-AM-600x269.png 600w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.13.53-AM-500x224.png 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1432px) 100vw, 1432px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Publish the page and your first category calendar is now ready on your website! Rinse and repeat for as many calendars as you like on your WordPress site.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"1048\" height=\"1266\" src=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.21.45-AM.png\" alt=\"How to add category shortcode on a WordPress site\" class=\"wp-image-2320787\" srcset=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.21.45-AM.png 1048w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.21.45-AM-248x300.png 248w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.21.45-AM-665x803.png 665w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.21.45-AM-70x85.png 70w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.21.45-AM-768x928.png 768w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.21.45-AM-430x519.png 430w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.21.45-AM-645x779.png 645w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.21.45-AM-460x556.png 460w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.21.45-AM-512x619.png 512w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.21.45-AM-912x1102.png 912w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.21.45-AM-439x530.png 439w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.21.45-AM-300x362.png 300w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.21.45-AM-600x725.png 600w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-18-at-11.21.45-AM-500x604.png 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1048px) 100vw, 1048px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-events-calendar-pro-shortcodes-for-the-win\">Events Calendar Pro shortcodes for the win</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s easy to create personalized calendars across your WordPress site with <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/products/wordpress-events-calendar/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Events Calendar Pro</a> in hand.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Love using shortcodes? We’ve got even more to share! Check out our <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/knowledgebase/k/events-calendar-pro-widget-shortcodes-overview/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">widget shortcodes</a> to add a calendar to sidebars, footers, and more. See available shortcodes for all of our products in our <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/knowledgebase/guide/shortcodes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Shortcodes Guide</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/blog/tips/how-to-use-shortcodes-to-create-multiple-calendars-on-your-wordpress-site/\">How to Use Shortcodes to Create Multiple Calendars on Your WordPress Site</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com\">The Events Calendar</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"Virtual Events 1.7.1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:80:\"https://theeventscalendar.com/release-notes/virtual-events/virtual-events-1-7-1/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 19 Oct 2021 17:56:31 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Virtual Events\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_expl