(1060, '_transient_jm_14793ec8ab2c9e2b6991f13d4119c3e41635289688', '{\"posts\":[{\"ID\":225,\"post_author\":\"1\",\"post_date\":\"2021-10-26 19:08:07\",\"post_date_gmt\":\"2021-10-26 23:08:07\",\"post_content\":\"<div class=\\\"jobsearch-DesktopTag\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"jobsearch-DesktopTag-tag urgently-hiring\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"jobsearch-DesktopTag-text\\\">Urgently hiring<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"mosaic-aboveExtractedJobDescription\\\" class=\\\"mosaic-zone\\\"><\\/div>\\n<div class=\\\"jobsearch-JobComponent-description jobsearch-JobComponent-description--embedded icl-u-xs-mb--md\\\">\\n<div id=\\\"mosaic-jobHighlights\\\" class=\\\"mosaic-zone\\\"><\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"mosaic-aboveFullJobDescription\\\" class=\\\"mosaic-zone\\\"><\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"jobDescriptionText\\\" class=\\\"jobsearch-jobDescriptionText\\\">\\n\\n<b>Rentsync<\\/b>\\u00a0provides h<b>igh quality websites, marketing services<\\/b>\\u00a0and\\u00a0<b>software solutions<\\/b>\\u00a0to the\\u00a0<b>rental and property management industry<\\/b>\\u00a0throughout Canada and the United States.\\n\\nWe are looking for a\\u00a0<b>Software Developer<\\/b>\\u00a0to join our product development team to contribute to the success of our growing software platforms and technology by working with our team to\\u00a0<b>monitor &amp; maintain, resolve bugs, improve code, enhance user experiences, and build new features &amp; functionality.<\\/b>\\n\\nYou will primarily use\\u00a0<b>TypeScript\\/JavaScript, NodeJS,\\u00a0<\\/b>and\\u00a0<b>VueJS<\\/b>\\u00a0while working with our software platforms for the Canadian housing and rental industry.\\n\\nWe have multiple smaller teams of developers and engineers working on different disciplines within our software ecosystem. Fit will be based on skills, experience, interest, and team need.\\n\\n<b>Looking for someone who has:<\\/b>\\n<ul>\\n \\t<li>Solid understanding of programming and building web applications<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<ul>\\n \\t