(60, 1, '2021-10-24 20:06:10', '2021-10-25 00:06:10', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><span class=\"has-inline-color has-vivid-red-color\">AFTER SCHOOL PROGRAM</span></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"full\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull is-style-default\"><img src=\"http://perrinsmartialarts.ca/img/header_afterschoolprogram.jpg\" alt=\"After School Program\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Let us pick your children up from school and make sure they get their daily exercise. Our after school program includes a daily martial arts class, and gives time for both a snack and homework.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our after school program uses a structured curriculum and built-in reward system to give children in Stoney Creek a platform to learn and develop confidence, respect, discipline, focus, and self esteem.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>AFTER SCHOOL SCHEDULE</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The after school program run the entire school year. We pick up from all schools in Stoney Creek in a marked, insured vehicle. Our route is based on school demand.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Halfway through the school year? Don’t worry, you can register your child anytime through the school year. Our preference will go to students interested in the monthly program.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For more information on our after school program,&nbsp;<a href=\"http://perrinsmartialarts.ca/pdf/after-school-brochure-2020.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>download our brochure</strong></a>&nbsp;or call 905-664-8949 to set up an appointment with a member of Perrins Martial Arts staff to receive your enrolment package.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ready to <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"http://perrinsmartialarts.ca/contact/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"http://perrinsmartialarts.ca/contact/\" target=\"_blank\">register</a> for a program?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"30px\"}}} -->\n<p style=\"font-size:30px\"><strong><span class=\"has-inline-color has-vivid-red-color\">ADULT SUMMER LEAGUES</span></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><img src=\"https://secureservercdn.net/198.71.233.33/yvs.a5e.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/outdoor1.jpg?time=1635227629\" alt=\"outdoor1\" style=\"width: 900px;\"><br><br>Adult summer soccer leagues are run by&nbsp;<a href=\"https://soccer-world.ca/contactus/\">Soccer World</a>, a sports organization and not a member of Ontario Soccer. As such, rules for return to play, fees and player books are different. Players will be required to sign the standard waiver and agree to Soccer World implemented COVID rules and protocols for safe play. Step 2 (July 2021) allows unlimited roster size, no mask requirements, no restrictions on game rules. First 11v11 games are scheduled for July 6 and 7v7 games on July 11.<br><br>Men\'s soccer, women\'s soccer and COED summer leagues will run outside. Small sided leagues will play on turf fields. A combinations of turf and grass fields will be used for 11v11 leagues. Men\'s leagues, COED and women\'s leagues will play at various locations.</td></tr><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><img width=\"400\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"https://secureservercdn.net/198.71.233.33/yvs.a5e.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/womens-summer.jpg 400w, https://secureservercdn.net/198.71.233.33/yvs.a5e.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/womens-summer-300x150.jpg 300w\" src=\"https://secureservercdn.net/198.71.233.33/yvs.a5e.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/womens-summer.jpg?time=1635227629\" alt=\"womens-summer\"></td><td><a href=\"https://www.amilia.com/store/en/soccer-world/shop/programs\"><strong>7v7</strong>&nbsp;Soccer</a><br>2x25min - unlimited roster size - COVID player limit TBD<br>Independent of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.ontariosoccer.net/\">Ontario Soccer</a><br>$2,100 (incl HST) - membership required<br>e-transfer, full payment discount<br><a href=\"https://www.amilia.com/store/en/soccer-world/shop/programs\"><strong>Team Registration</strong></a></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><br><a href=\"https://www.amilia.com/store/en/soccer-world/shop/programs\"><strong>11v11</strong>&nbsp;Soccer</a><br>2x40min - unlimited roster size - COVID player limit TBD<br>Independent of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.ontariosoccer.net/\">Ontario Soccer</a><br>$3,200 (incl HST) - membership required<br>e-transfer, full payment discount<br><a href=\"https://www.amilia.com/store/en/soccer-world/shop/programs\"><strong>Team Registration</strong></a></td><td><img width=\"400\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"https://secureservercdn.net/198.71.233.33/yvs.a5e.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/outdoor4.jpg 400w, https://secureservercdn.net/198.71.233.33/yvs.a5e.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/outdoor4-300x150.jpg 300w\" src=\"https://secureservercdn.net/198.71.233.33/yvs.a5e.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/outdoor4.jpg?time=1635227629\" alt=\"outdoor4\"></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"full\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignfull\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:table {\"align\":\"full\",\"className\":\"is-style-regular\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table alignfull is-style-regular\"><table><tbody><tr><td><span class=\"has-inline-color has-vivid-red-color\"><strong>WELCOME TO PERRINS MARTIAL ARTS I