al and Timely</span></strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Whatever subject we’re covering, the story is news. With our accessible takes on current events, scientific discoveries, new book and movie releases, and more, your kids may be the ones keeping you up to date.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong><span class=\"has-inline-color has-vivid-red-color\">A Wide Range of Reporting</span></strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>There’s something in these pages to delight and inspire every child—from sports, science, nature, and culture to engaging interactive features like weekly debates, how-to craft projects, recipes, and puzzles.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong><span class=\"has-inline-color has-vivid-red-color\">Published with Purpose</span></strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Clear, compelling headlines draw readers in,&nbsp;short blocks of text offer amazing facts kids can memorize and share—and special features help build their vocabulary and make them smile.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#000000\"}},\"fontSize\":\"extra-small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-extra-small-font-size\" style=\"color:#000000\">.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"40px\"}}} -->\n<p style=\"font-size:40px\"><strong><span class=\"has-inline-color has-vivid-red-color\">Articles</span></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><img src=\"https://imagesvc.meredithcorp.io/v3/mm/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.onecms.io%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F6%2F2021