-->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>An assessment is needed if you or your client</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>needs a Grade 12 equivalent to reach your/their goals</li><li>is 18+ and have been out of school for at least one year</li><li>is comfortable reading various materials, writing essays, and can perform basic math operations and work with decimals, fractions, algebra and geometry (if you/your client are not comfortable with all of these skills an EPAT is recommended)</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Educational Interviews</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Fee $50</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is an in-person meeting with an assessor with no assessment activities. &nbsp;In this meeting educational options and preferences will be discussed based on the education and employment goals. &nbsp;It will include an action plan to reach the client’s goals.&nbsp; This service is typically offered onsite with community partners.&nbsp; For more information, please contact us.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"http://www.ilc.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"></a>ABEA is a recognized by the Independent Learning Centre (ILC) as a GED preparation centre. For more GED test details including registration packages and test dates visit&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.ilc.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ilc.org</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Assessment Referral Process – for agencies</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"http://abea.on.ca/refer-a-client/\"><strong>To refer a client please complete the online referral form.</strong></a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you are unsure of which service to refer to, please call us so we can help.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>After we receive the referral form we will</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>connect with the client</li><li>ensure that the assessment you have chosen is appropriate</li><li>book an assessment time</li><li>email you back with the details of the appointment</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you do not hear back from us within 2 business days please call to ensure your referral was received.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Please note:</strong>&nbsp;clients who speak English as a second or additional language need to be at a Canadian Language Benchmark (CLB) 6 or higher (testing completed in the last 12 months) in Speaking and Listening to be appropriate for any of ABEA’s assessments. This is to ensure that the client can communicate clearly through the interview process. If the client does not have a current CLB test, please call ABEA for CLB testing details (ABEA does not provide this service).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Once the client is booked ABEA will</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>give the client a reminder call the day before the appointment</li><li>confirm the client’s attendance after the appointment time</li><li>forward the report when it is completed</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->', 'Assessment', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '81-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-10-24 22:34:51', '2021-10-25 02:34:51', '', 81, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=87', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
