dwich IslandsSouth KoreaSouth SudanSpainSri LankaSudanSurinameSvalbard and Jan MayenSwazilandSwedenSwitzerlandSyriaTaiwanTajikistanTanzaniaThailandTimor-LesteTogoTokelauTongaTrinidad and TobagoTunisiaTurkeyTurkmenistanTurks and Caicos IslandsTuvaluUgandaUkraineUnited Arab EmiratesUnited Kingdom (UK)United States (US)United States (US) Minor Outlying IslandsUnited States (US) Virgin IslandsUruguayUzbekistanVanuatuVaticanVenezuelaVietnamWallis and FutunaWestern SaharaYemenZambiaZimbabweHow did you hear about our online workshops?– Select –Teach2030 Facebook PageTeach2030 WebsiteTeach2030 EmailWord of MouthTeach2030 AmbassadorSubmit Form</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Highlights from our previous workshops</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Below are some short highlights from our previous workshops to give you a flavour of what to expect in our 15-minute sessions. Also, if you click on the yellow button below that will take you to our workshop archive page where you will find full recordings and additional activities from our previous workshops.https://www.youtube.com/embed/1YQ9N4AQ7Bo?enablejsapi=1&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=0&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;autohide=2&amp;theme=dark&amp;color=red&amp;controls=1&amp;https://www.youtube.com/embed/FMwR6INJY8E?enablejsapi=1&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=0&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;autohide=2&amp;theme=dark&amp;color=red&amp;controls=1&amp;https://www.youtube.com/embed/Fhww2ajpChk?enablejsapi=1&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=0&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;autohide=2&amp;theme=dark&amp;color=red&amp;controls=1&amp;<a href=\"https://teach2030.com/online-workshops/archive/\"><strong>Access our full archive</strong>&nbsp;<strong>of recordings and resources</strong></a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Our workshop hosts</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":26914} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://teach2030.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Team_Eleanor-picture-500x500-removebg-preview.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-26914\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>Eleanor Sykes</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Over twenty years teaching ensures Eleanor has a true understanding of challenges faced by teachers, and what good classroom practice looks like in any setting worldwide. Her desire to support teachers in low-income countries means she has spent considerable time in schools, observing and discussing with teachers their classroom practice and how CPD materials could help.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":26974} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://teach2030.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Alex-Starr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-26974\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>Alexandra Starr</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Alexandra is an education, teaching and learning specialist, who is passionate about the English language. She supports content by course writing, editing, and proof-reading. She also focuses on communication with our learners, by designing blogs and social media.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":23512,\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https://commonwealtheducationtrust.org/\"><img src=\"https://teach2030.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Logo.-Vector.-HIGH-RES.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-23512\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Teach2030 is brought to you by the Commonwealth Education Trust. We are a registered Commonwealth charity committed to tackling the UN’s Sustainable Development Goal 4: Ensure quality education for all. Working in partnerships across our Commonwealth network of 54 countries.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://teach2030.com/contact/\">CONTACT US</a><br><a href=\"mailto:hello@commonwealtheducationtrust.org\">hello@teach2030.com</a><br>+44 (0)20 3096 7721<br>7-14 Great Dover Street, London, SE1 4YR</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://teach2030.com/privacy-policy/\">Privacy Policy / Disclaimer / Terms of Use</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Join the Teach2030 community</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/teach2030\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">facebook</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyLOxroDVZFgN1N_GdvsPdg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">youtube</a></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://teach2030.com/group-management/\">Group Management</a>© 2020 Commonwealth Education Trust. All Rights Reserved. Registered Charity Number: 1119647</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Consulting Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '94-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-10-25 00:45:25', '2021-10-25 04:45:25', '', 94, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=99', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
