her expenses related to your post-secondary education. You can apply to support your first year as well as subsequent years of studies at college or university.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To be considered for bursaries available at HCF, students must submit their bursary application directly to us, using the links below.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure id=\"tablepress-13\" class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Subject/program</strong></td><td><strong>School (CRA -approved)</strong></td><td><strong>Bursary</strong></td><td><strong>How to apply</strong></td><td><strong>Application deadline(s)</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Any</td><td>Canada or USA</td><td><a href=\"https://www.hamiltoncommunityfoundation.ca/impact/stories/chaney-ensign-bursary-fund/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Chaney-Ensign Bursary</a></td><td><a href=\"https://www.grantrequest.com/SID_5831?SA=SNA&amp;FID=35020\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Here</a></td><td>October 1<br>February 1</td></tr><tr><td>Music</td><td>Canada or abroad</td><td><a href=\"https://www.hamiltoncommunityfoundation.ca/impact/stories/david-davis-memorial-fund/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">David Davis Memorial Bursary</a></td><td><a href=\"https://www.grantrequest.com/SID_5831?SA=SNA&amp;FID=35016\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Here</a></td><td>October 1</td></tr><tr><td>Performing arts (voice, drama, dance<br>or a musical instrument)</td><td>Canada or USA</td><td><a href=\"https://www.hamiltoncommunityfoundation.ca/impact/stories/the-geritol-follies/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Geritol Follies Bursary</a></td><td><a href=\"https://www.grantrequest.com/SID_5831?SA=SNA&amp;FID=35015\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Here</a></td><td>October 1</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Selection criteria for these awards are:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Student must demonstrate financial need through OSAP application</li><li>Student must be registered and enrolled full-time</li><li>For Chaney-Ensign, student must be a graduate of a publicly funded high school in Hamilton</li><li>For Geritol Follies, student must be a graduate of a publicly funded high school in Hamilton or Burlington</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Note: all applicants will be asked to submit information about their expenses associated with attending post-secondary as well as a verification of financial need from their student financial aid office.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Use Internet Explorer, Mozilla Firefox or Apple Safari to open the application – Google Chrome will not work</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Make sure you have the following before you begin your application:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Social Insurance Number</li><li>Student number</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Make sure you have the following ready to upload as attachments:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Your OSAP Funding Summary</li><li>Statement of tuition payment for current semester (or full academic year if available)</li><li>Transcript of final secondary school marks&nbsp;<em>(first-time applicants only)</em></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For questions about these bursaries or the online application process, please contact us at 905.523.5600</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Student awards available at post-secondary institutions</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>HCF also offers several student awards through post-secondary institutions. In most cases, students apply through their financial aid office for consideration.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em><strong>McMaster University</strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Important:&nbsp;</strong>Please read the guidelines&nbsp;<a href=\"https://academiccalendars.romcmaster.ca/content.php?catoid=32&amp;navoid=7828\">here</a>&nbsp;about accessing student award funding through McMaster’s Financial Aid Office.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em><strong>Bursaries:</strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure id=\"tablepress-14\" class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Subject/program</strong></td><td><strong>Name of award</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Any</td><td>Ross F. Webb Bursary</td></tr><tr><td>Any</td><td>Russell &amp; Elizabeth Lindley Bursary</td></tr><tr><td>Business, Commerce, or Management<br><em>(available for students in the DeGroote School of Business)</em></td><td>Bernie Morelli Memorial Bursary*</td></tr><tr><td>Music</td><td>Hamilton Community Foundation Music Bursary</td></tr><tr><td>Undergraduate Medical&nbsp;<em>(available for students in the<br>Michael G. DeGroote School of Medicine)</em></td><td>Frank C. Miller Jr. Bursary</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em><strong>Scholarships:</strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure id=\"tablepress-16\" class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Subject/program</strong></td><td><strong>Name of award</strong></td></tr><tr><td>To support studies outside North America<br><em>(where English is not the first language)</em></td><td>Rundle Foreign Study Scholarship*</td></tr><tr><td>This fund supports a full-time, post-doctoral student in the sciences at McMaster University. &nbsp;Visit the McMaster website for information about applying,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://gs.mcmaster.ca/current-students/scholarships/eb-eastburn/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">here</a>.</td><td>The E.B. Eastburn Postdoctoral Fellowship Fund</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em><strong>Mohawk College</strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Important:</strong>&nbsp;please read the guidelines&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mohawkcollege.ca/student-life-at-mohawk/financial-assistance/awards-scholarships-and-bursaries/how-to-apply-for\">here</a>&nbsp;about accessing bursary funding through Mohawk’s Financial Aid Office.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>General application bursaries:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure id=\"tablepress-17\" class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Subject/program</strong></td><td><strong>Name of award</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Child and Youth Care<br>Early Childhood Education<br>Educational Support<br>Social Service Worker<br>Engineering (various programs)</td><td>Charlie and Mabel Duncan Memorial Bursary*</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>*preference will be given to graduates of publicly funded Hamilton high schools.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><br>Other awards available</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For some of our student awards, there is&nbsp;<strong><em>no application required as the faculty selects the recipients</em></strong>&nbsp;on HCF’s behalf. Details of these awards are listed below:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em><strong>McMaster University</strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure id=\"tablepress-64\" class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Subject/program</strong></td><td><strong>Name of award</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Manufacturing Engineering</td><td>Grace Dorothy &amp; William P. Carpenter scholarship award</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em><strong>Mohawk College</strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure id=\"tablepress-18\" class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Subject/program</strong></td><td><strong>Name of award</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Tool and Die Design</td><td>Grace Dorothy Carpenter Award**</td></tr><tr><td>Tool and Die Design</td><td>William P. Carpenter Award**</td></tr><tr><td>Mechanical and Industrial Technology</td><td>Phyllis Mary Carpenter Award**</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em><strong>University of Guelph</strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure id=\"tablepress-19\" class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Subject/program</strong></td><td><strong>Name of award</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Environmental Engineering</td><td>Phyllis Mary Carpenter Award**</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>**<em>preference given to the graduates of publicly funded high schools in Hamilton or Burlington</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>** For detailed information click <a href=\"https://scholarship-grants.org/hamilton-community-foundation-student-bursaries-for-high-school-students/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://scholarship-grants.org/hamilton-community-foundation-student-bursaries-for-high-school-students/\">here</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Scholarship & Bursaries', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '57-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-10-25 16:34:01', '2021-10-25 20:34:01', '', 57, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=147', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
