(281, 1, '2021-10-27 00:07:57', '2021-10-27 04:07:57', '<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.amilia.com/store/en/soccer-world/shop/programs/68458?subCategoryIds=3533879&amp;subCategoryIds=3533867&amp;subCategoryIds=3533858&amp;subCategoryIds=3533852&amp;subCategoryIds=3533849\">Soccer&nbsp;<strong>Classes</strong></a></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":7184,\"linkDestination\":\"custom\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><a href=\"https://www.amilia.com/store/en/soccer-world/shop/programs/68458?subCategoryIds=3533879&amp;subCategoryIds=3533867&amp;subCategoryIds=3533858&amp;subCategoryIds=3533852&amp;subCategoryIds=3533849\"><img src=\"https://secureservercdn.net/198.71.233.33/yvs.a5e.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/classes-with-dads.jpg\" alt=\"classes-with-dads\" class=\"wp-image-7184\" title=\"classes-with-dads\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>17mos - 6yrs</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Soccer classes are a child development program using soccer. Parent involvement classes (17mos - 3yrs) use creative games to develop agility, balance and basic understanding of soccer balls, noodles, cones and other fun items. Beginner classes (3yrs - 6yrs) introduce soccer game play with a series of fun activities and creative games that encourage the kind of imagination that appeals to this age group. Classes are non-competitive using age appropriate games and logical skill progressions.<a href=\"https://www.amilia.com/store/en/soccer-world/shop/programs/68458?subCategoryIds=3533879&amp;subCategoryIds=3533867&amp;subCategoryIds=3533858&amp;subCategoryIds=3533852&amp;subCategoryIds=3533849\">Register NOW</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.amilia.com/store/en/soccer-world/shop/programs/68458?subCategoryIds=3533931&amp;subCategoryIds=3533925&amp;subCategoryIds=3533917&amp;subCategoryIds=3533909&amp;subCategoryIds=3533900&amp;subCategoryIds=3533894\">Soccer&nbsp;<strong>Clinics</strong></a></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":7187,\"linkDestination\":\"custom\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><a href=\"https://www.amilia.com/store/en/soccer-world/shop/programs/68458?subCategoryIds=3533931&amp;subCategoryIds=3533925&amp;subCategoryIds=3533917&amp;subCategoryIds=3533909&amp;subCategoryIds=3533900&amp;subCategoryIds=3533894\"><img src=\"https://secureservercdn.net/198.71.233.33/yvs.a5e.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/clinic-scrimmage.jpg\" alt=\"clinic-scrimmage\" class=\"wp-image-7187\" title=\"clinic-scrimmage\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>5yrs - 15yrs</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Skills clinics follow proven pre-designed weekly lesson plans led by coaches who are skilled soccer players. They are selected for their energy and love of teaching children. We deliver technical instruction, tons of ball touches, and a passion for the game. Soccer clinics are adapted for all skill levels and ages. From the soccer warm-up to the scrimmage our coaches are actively involved. The energy level is infectious and guaranteed to put a smile on every face.<a href=\"https://www.amilia.com/store/en/soccer-world/shop/programs/68458?subCategoryIds=3533931&amp;subCategoryIds=3533925&amp;subCategoryIds=3533917&amp;subCategoryIds=3533909&amp;subCategoryIds=3533900&amp;subCategoryIds=3533894\">Register NOW</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.amilia.com/store/en/soccer-world/shop/programs/68458?subCategoryIds=3533985&amp;subCategoryIds=3533979&amp;subCategoryIds=3533973&amp;subCategoryIds=3533967&amp;subCategoryIds=3533953&amp;subCategoryIds=3533935\">Soccer&nbsp;<strong>Leagues</strong></a></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":7192,\"linkDestination\":\"custom\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><a href=\"https://www.amilia.com/store/en/soccer-world/shop/programs/68458?subCategoryIds=3533985&amp;subCategoryIds=3533979&amp;subCategoryIds=3533973&amp;subCategoryIds=3533967&amp;subCategoryIds=3533953&amp;subCategoryIds=3533935\"><img src=\"https://secureservercdn.net/198.71.233.33/yvs.a5e.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/u17g.jpg\" alt=\"u17g\" class=\"wp-image-7192\" title=\"u17g\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>u6 - u17</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Youth soccer leagues are all action. Designed to keep everyone involved and generate lots of touches. With small-sided 4v4 games, the youngest players have coaches on the field assisting and guiding. While the high school age players play the indoor game with adult referees and sideline coaching. Key across all leagues is the principle of fair and equal play. Popular with player and parents alike, the energy level is always high.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Fair Play - Equal Time</strong><a href=\"https://www.amilia.com/store/en/soccer-world/shop/programs/68458?subCategoryIds=3533985&amp;subCategoryIds=3533979&amp;subCategoryIds=3533973&amp;subCategoryIds=3533967&amp;subCategoryIds=3533953&amp;subCategoryIds=3533935\">Register NOW</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Sports', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '60-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-10-27 00:07:57', '2021-10-27 04:07:57', '', 60, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=281', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(283, 1, '2021-10-27 00:12:59', '2021-10-27 04:12:59', '<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>Adult <strong>Summer Leagues</strong><br><br><img width=\"400\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"https://secureservercdn.net/198.71.233.33/yvs.a5e.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/outdoor1.jpg 400w, https://secureservercdn.net/198.71.233.33/yvs.a5e.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/outdoor1-300x150.jpg 300w\" src=\"https://secureservercdn.net/198.71.233.33/yvs.a5e.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/outdoor1.jpg?time=1635227629\" alt=\"outdoor1\"><br><br>Adult summer soccer leagues are run by <a href=\"https://soccer-world.ca/contactus/\">Soccer World</a>, a sports organization and not a member of Ontario Soccer. As such, rules for return to play, fees and player books are different. Players will be required to sign the standard waiver and agree to Soccer World implemented COVID rules and protocols for safe play. Step 2 (July 2021) allows unlimited roster size, no mask requirements, no restrictions on game rules. First 11v11 games are scheduled for July 6 and 7v7 games on July 11.<br><br>Men\'s soccer, women\'s soccer and COED summer leagues will run outside. Small sided leagues will play on turf fields. A combinations of turf and grass fields will be used for 11v11 leagues. Men\'s leagues, COED and women\'s leagues will play at various locations.</td></tr><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><img width=\"400\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"https://secureservercdn.net/198.71.233.33/yvs.a5e.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/womens-summer.jpg 400w, https://secureservercdn.net/198.71.233.33/yvs.a5e.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/womens-summer-300x150.jpg 300w\" src=\"https://secureservercdn.net/198.71.233.33/yvs.a5e.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/womens-summer.jpg?time=1635227629\" alt=\"womens-s