es a structured curriculum and built-in reward system to give children in Stoney Creek a platform to learn and develop confidence, respect, discipline, focus, and self esteem.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>AFTER SCHOOL SCHEDULE</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The after school program run the entire school year. We pick up from all schools in Stoney Creek in a marked, insured vehicle. Our route is based on school demand.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Halfway through the school year? Don’t worry, you can register your child anytime through the school year. Our preference will go to students interested in the monthly program.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For more information on our after school program,&nbsp;<a href=\"http://perrinsmartialarts.ca/pdf/after-school-brochure-2020.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>download our brochure</strong></a>&nbsp;or call 905-664-8949 to set up an appointment with a member of Perrins Martial Arts staff to receive your enrolment package.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ready to <a href=\"http://perrinsmartialarts.ca/contact/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"http://perrinsmartialarts.ca/contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">register</a> for a program?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"full\",\"id\":286,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full is-style-default\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Hamont-Sports-Soccer-Football-Header-V2-scaled-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-286\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', 'Sports', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '60-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-10-27 00:23:18', '2021-10-27 04:23:18', '', 60, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=289', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
