<br>2x25min - unlimited roster size - COVID player limit TBD<br>Independent of <a href=\"https://www.ontariosoccer.net/\">Ontario Soccer</a><br>$2,100 (incl HST) - membership required<br>e-transfer, full payment discount<br><a href=\"https://www.amilia.com/store/en/soccer-world/shop/programs\"><strong>Team Registration</strong></a></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><br><a href=\"https://www.amilia.com/store/en/soccer-world/shop/programs\"><strong>11v11</strong> Soccer</a><br>2x40min - unlimited roster size - COVID player limit TBD<br>Independent of <a href=\"https://www.ontariosoccer.net/\">Ontario Soccer</a><br>$3,200 (incl HST) - membership required<br>e-transfer, full payment discount<br><a href=\"https://www.amilia.com/store/en/soccer-world/shop/programs\"><strong>Team Registration</strong></a></td><td><img width=\"400\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"https://secureservercdn.net/198.71.233.33/yvs.a5e.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/outdoor4.jpg 400w, https://secureservercdn.net/198.71.233.33/yvs.a5e.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/outdoor4-300x150.jpg 300w\" src=\"https://secureservercdn.net/198.71.233.33/yvs.a5e.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/outdoor4.jpg?time=1635227629\" alt=\"outdoor4\"></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1>AFTER SCHOOL PROGRAM</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"full\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull is-style-default\"><img src=\"http://perrinsmartialarts.ca/img/header_afterschoolprogram.jpg\" alt=\"After School Program\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Let us pick your children up from school and make sure they get their daily exercise. Our after school program includes a daily martial arts class, and gives time for both a snack and homework.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our after school program uses a structured curriculum and built-in reward system to give children in Stoney Creek a platform to learn and develop confidence, respect, discipline, focus, and self esteem.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>AFTER SCHOOL SCHEDULE</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The after school program run the entire school year. We pick up from all schools in Stoney Creek in a marked, insured vehicle. Our route is based on school demand.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Halfway through the school year? Don’t worry, you can register your child anytime through the school year. Our preference will go to students interested in the monthly program.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For more information on our after school program,&nbsp;<a href=\"http://perrinsmartialarts.ca/pdf/after-school-brochure-2020.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>download our brochure</strong></a>&nbsp;or call 905-664-8949 to set up an appointment with a member of Perrins Martial Arts staff to receive your enrolment package.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ready to <a href=\"http://perrinsmartialarts.ca/contact/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"http://perrinsmartialarts.ca/contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">register</a> for a program?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"full\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignfull\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:table {\"align\":\"full\",\"className\":\"is-style-regular\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table alignfull is-style-regular\"><table><tbody><tr><td><span class=\"has-inline-color has-vivid-red-color\"><strong>WELCOME TO PERRINS MARTIAL ARTS IN STONEY CREEK</strong></span><br><br>Perrins Martial Arts provides Stoney Creek and Hamilton children, youth and adults with the finest martial art instruction; providing safe, fun classes for any age group. By joining Perrins Martial Arts, you’re joining almost 300 other families that practice with us and train under our world class instructors.<br>Perrins Martial Arts offers classes for the whole family, from ages 3 through adult. With classes in martial arts, cardio kickboxing, Brazilian Jiu Jitsu and kickboxing, our fitness centre offers the finest in Hamilton and Stoney Creek martial art instruction.<br><br><br><br><strong><span class=\"has-inline-color has-vivid-red-color\">ARE MARTIAL ARTS FOR YOU?</span></strong><br>Our classes are taught by world class instructors who welcome you to drop by and watch a class to see if martial arts are for you or your children.<br><br></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:embed {\"url\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mywJ33_l6zk\\u0026t=3s\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"responsive\":true,\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mywJ33_l6zk&amp;t=3s\n</div></figure>\n<!-- /wp:embed --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"full\",\"id\":286,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full is-style-default\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Hamont-Sports-Soccer-Football-Header-V2-scaled-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-286\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', 'Sports', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '60-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-10-27 00:38:51', '2021-10-27 04:38:51', '', 60, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=295', 0, 'revision', '', 0